# =============================================================================
# This Git repository is rooted at the HOME directory (/home/ywlee).
# To avoid ever committing shell config, SSH keys, cloud credentials, or AI
# tool state, we IGNORE EVERYTHING by default and then explicitly re-include
# only the MetricLens project files below. Add new top-level project paths
# with a matching "!/path" line.
# =============================================================================
/*

# --- Tracked project files ---
!/.gitignore
!/.gcloudignore
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/cloudbuild.yaml
!/usenix2022.docx
!/backend/
!/frontend/
!/docs/
!/scripts/
!/MetricLens_AI/

# --- Build artifacts / caches inside tracked directories ---
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.db
*.sqlite3
backend/.venv/
backend/.pytest_cache/
backend/.ruff_cache/
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
*.swp
